WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:14.677 --> 00:00:18.415
"1994 Mumbai, sorry Bombay...

00:00:19.197 --> 00:00:20.173
At that time it was called Bombay."

00:00:32.330 --> 00:00:33.602
I want to start my own business...

00:00:35.156 --> 00:00:35.892
I wanna be rich.

00:00:39.039 --> 00:00:40.044
I wanna be a top model.

00:00:42.256 --> 00:00:42.897
Bulbul Singh.

00:00:46.981 --> 00:00:47.840
Shall we open a bar?

00:00:51.591 --> 00:00:53.985
Lets make a film...starring
Madhuri and me?

00:01:03.169 --> 00:01:07.053
"All it takes to set up a big
business is a big idea."

00:01:07.946 --> 00:01:08.838
Well, I got that big idea.

00:01:28.321 --> 00:01:28.822
Then lets do it...

00:01:36.619 --> 00:01:37.917
I promise you once you have
done business with us...

00:01:38.125 --> 00:01:39.990
...you will never do business again.

00:01:40.257 --> 00:01:40.762
Sorry?

00:01:41.177 --> 00:01:41.895
With anybody else.

00:02:12.479 --> 00:02:14.729
You know one day I'll become
the richest man on the earth.

00:02:17.033 --> 00:02:18.104
How rich do you want to become?

00:02:18.309 --> 00:02:19.076
This is just the beginning.

00:02:28.285 --> 00:02:31.452
"All it takes to set up a big
business is a big idea."

